comments: Hield (IND) makes marginal body contact with Avdija (WAS) as he is driving towards the rim.
Avdija (WAS) makes marginal contact with Brissett (IND) in the post.
Avdija (WAS) slightly extends his arm into Brissett (IND) and makes marginal contact as he go for the loose ball.
Kispert (WAS) maintains a legal vertical position during Haliburton's (IND) shot attempt.
Avdija (WAS) does not maintain a legal vertical position when contesting Taylor's (IND) shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) and Haliburton (IND) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound.
Haliburton (IND) engages and disengages with Neto (WAS) as he cut towards the ball. The contact is marginal and did not affect Neto's ability to defend the ball.
Avdija (WAS) commits a personal take foul against Hield (IND).
Caldwell-Pope (WAS) commits a personal take foul against Hield (IND).
Hield (IND) briefly makes marginal contact to Kuzma's (WAS) body as he goes up for his shot near the rim.
Kuzma (WAS) commits a personal take foul against Haliburton (IND).
